<p>Method 1:</p>  <pre><code>Mongo mongo = new Mongo(); DB db = mongo.getDB("db"); DBCollection collection = db.getCollection("collection"); </code></pre>  <p>Method 2:</p>  <pre><code>MongoClient client = new MongoClient("localhost", 27017); MongoDatabase db = client.getDatabase("db"); MongoCollection&lt;Document&gt; collection = db.getCollection("collection"); </code></pre>  <p>Which is the preferred method and why? What are the advantages to either method?</p>